---
// OptiCV Final CTA Band

---

<div class="bg-primary-600 py-20">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
		<h2 class="font-headings text-4xl font-bold text-white lg:text-5xl">
			Your next interview is one upload away.
		</h2>
		<p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl text-lg text-primary-100">
			Give your CV the edge it deserves — free to try, no credit card.
		</p>
		<div class="mt-8">
			<a
				href="/"
				class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors hover:bg-accent-400"
			>
				Optimize my CV
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
